      "description": "GPU utilization. NOTE: requires external exporter — node-exporter does NOT expose GPU metrics. Install nvidia-gpu-exporter (https://github.com/utkuozdemir/nvidia_gpu_exporter) or DCGM exporter, then this panel will populate. Without the exporter the panel stays empty.",
